---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  path="/legal/privacy"
  description="Privacy policy for Mecker Capital website."
  robots="noindex,follow"
>
  <article class="section-card reveal max-w-3xl p-6 md:p-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
      <p>
        This website is designed to collect minimal personal data. There is no on-site email capture form in this version.
      </p>
      <p>
        Basic aggregate traffic analytics are processed through Vercel Analytics to understand site performance and content
        reach. These metrics are used for operational insights only.
      </p>
      <p>
        External links to Substack, X, and YouTube are governed by those platforms' own privacy policies.
      </p>
      <p>
        If this policy changes, updates will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> February 11, 2026.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
